sections.Trivia:
- This is the last episode where Atsuko Tanaka voiced Chihaya Hagiwara, as she passed away on August 20, 2024.
- When Jugo recalls that Enzaki was reading book while waiting for his turn, there is drawing error where both Jugo and Enzaki did not wear mask.
- In both episodes, Itaru Kaburagi's name is wrongly spelled as "Itaru Kaburaki" (かぶらき いたる).
- The suspects' names are related to "marriage"[1] :
Anju Tomari (泊里 安珠) comes from "mariage" (マリアージュ ,Mariāju?), while her real name Ari Sukiyama (鋤山 有梨) comes from (marriage) scammer (スキャマー ,Sukyamā?) ;
Ikuhisa Uedera (上寺 幾久) comes from "wedding" (ウェディング ,Uedingu?) ;
Genji Enzaki (円崎 源司) comes from (to be) engage(d) (エンゲージ ,Engēji?) ;
Itaru Kaburagi (蕪木 到) comes from bridals (ブライダル ,buraidaru?).
